sentences.english: Red strains of Delicious are being planted.
sentences.chinese: 元帅的红色品系也有栽植。

sentences.english: The second was a group of vociferous Air Marshales.
sentences.chinese: 第二股势力是一批气壮如牛的空军元帅。

sentences.english: The principle proponent of the Deep Operations theory, Marshal of the Soviet Union, Mikhail Tukhachevsky.
sentences.chinese: 大纵深战略理论的倡导者，苏联元帅，图哈切夫斯基。

sentences.english: If he failed, Palpatine threatened to behead the Grand Admiral.
sentences.chinese: 如果他失败，帕尔帕丁威胁要对这位元帅处以斩首。

sentences.english: Field Marshal Keitel described her appearance during an interrogation at Nuremberg.
sentences.chinese: 在纽伦堡一次提审时，凯特尔元帅描述了她的形象。

sentences.english: He entered the marshal's apartment while I was there.
sentences.chinese: 我在元帅房间里的时候，他进来了。

sentences.english: Marshal Zhukov's contribution to the Great Patriotic War is unparalleled to anyone.
sentences.chinese: 朱可夫元帅为伟大卫国战争胜利做出的贡献无人能及。

sentences.english: Zhukov was a marshal of the former Soviet Union.
sentences.chinese: 朱可夫是前苏联的一位元帅。

sentences.english: Every French soldier carries a marshal's baton in his knapsack.
sentences.chinese: 每个法国士兵的背包里都装着一只元帅的权杖。

sentences.english: Can we speak on your behalf to the king or the commander of the army?
sentences.chinese: 你向王或元帅有所求的没有？

sentences.english: Then she handed the package to Marshal.
At once I noticed that field marshal's face continuously twitches.
sentences.chinese: 我立刻就注意到，这位陆军元帅的脸在不断抽搐。

sentences.english: The Marshal stepped over the vacuum- cleaner and stumped out of the room.
sentences.chinese: 元帅迈过真空吸尘器，脚步沉重地走出了房间。

sentences.english: The Admiral and successor of the Fuhrer will now speak to the German people. In his speech, Admiral Doenitz said
sentences.chinese: 海军元帅兼元首继承人现在将对德国人民讲话。
